==================================================

Maya and Nuke python tools for Windows and Linux.

==================================================

REQUIREMENTS:
- NukeX.X and MayaX installed
- python2.5+ installed in c:/python27

INSTALL:
- clone dmptools: git clone git://github.com/michael-ha/dmptools.git
- in command shell go to the root of the dmptools and run 'python install.py'
or
- clone dmptools: git clone git://github.com/michael-ha/dmptools.git
- open Sublime Text
- project > open > dmptools.sublime-project
- open dmptools/installFromSublime.py
- tools > build system > dmptools
- tools > build

RESULT:
In Maya you should now see a new shelf
In Nuke you should now see a new toolbar